POSTADMIN: A tool for postfix's workaround.org configuration CLI management

Requirements:

Managing 
- domains: add, delete
- users, alias: add, delete, update

CLI examples:

postadm add alias newalias@otherdomain.tld target@domain.com	# Add newalias@otherdomain.tld as an alias for target@domain.com
postadm delete domain domaintodelete.fr				# Delete domain
postadm add email -p"è789hsgj_Tg" -q 20M -e me@example.com	# Create email me@example.com with plain password è789hsgj_Tg and a quota of 20MB 
postadm add email me@example.com "è789hsgj_Tg" 1G		# Create email me@example.com with plain password è789hsgj_Tg and a quota of 1GB
postadm delete email me@example.com				# Delete email me@example.com
postadm suspend email me@example.com 3d				# Suspend email me@example.com for 3 days

SYNOPSIS
  postadm [action] [type] [options]
